### ============================================================================
### PROJECT-LIST-API-006 | 분석 job 상태 저장
### Source of truth: Notion HTML export (source-confirmed)
### Endpoint: PATCH /api/list/analysis/{job_id}/status
### 관련 기능 ID: PROJECT-LIST-B-301, PROJECT-LIST-F-203
### 공개 범위: 내부 API / 서버 간 호출 전용
### ============================================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@serviceToken = replace-me-service-token
@jobId = 8f2d5a3c-b1a9-4d2c-9a3e-7f8a9b0c1d2e

### [정상] 실패 상태 저장
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/list/analysis/{{jobId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{serviceToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "failed",
  "currentStep": "CODE_MAP",
  "progress": 45,
  "message": "코드 구조 분석 중 오류가 발생했습니다.",
  "errorMessage": "File limit exceeded during parse stage."
}

### 200 OK
### {"code":200,"message":"success","data":{"jobId":"8f2d5a3c-b1a9-4d2c-9a3e-7f8a9b0c1d2e","status":"failed","currentStep":"CODE_MAP","progress":45,"updatedAt":"2026-06-18T02:05:00Z"}}
### status: queued | running | completed | failed
### currentStep: CLONE | CODE_MAP | DOC_GEN | ONBOARDING | REPORT
### 저장 규칙:
### - running -> IN_PROGRESS, completed -> COMPLETED, failed -> FAILED
### - failed이면 analysis_jobs.message에 errorMessage 우선 저장, 아니면 message 저장
### - progress는 0..100, updatedAt은 서버 시각

### [오류] 허용되지 않는 진행률
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/list/analysis/{{jobId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{serviceToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"status":"running","progress":101}

### 오류: 400 INVALID_STATUS, 400 INVALID_PROGRESS, 401 UNAUTHORIZED,
###       404 JOB_NOT_FOUND, 500 DATABASE_ERROR
